      ^  |                |
      ^  |----   ---|-----+
      ^  | @@64 Dorter   Nec |  @@64: Stairs
      ^  |----   ---|-----+
      ^  |    Lay Dorm    |
      ^  +----------------+^";

    Slype, Infirmary, InfirmaryChapel, Herbarium, Garden:
