      "A small alcove off the Cloister where the brothers wash before
      entering the Refectory. You can only go back the way you came.
      A basin is built into the wall.",
    n_to CloisterSW,
    cant_go "You can only go north.",
    cheap_scenery
      1 'peg' "It's just a peg for the towel."
    ,
  has
     ;


! TODO: maybe remove water? it's a pain to get things wet
! we can explain as forgotten under today's circumstances

Object -> Basin "basin"                                                 ! >Basin
