      A painted panel on the wall depicts
      the hours of the Divine Offices. In one corner stands a life-sized
      wooden statue. The only exit is to the west.",
    w_to CloisterNE,
    out_to CloisterNE,
    before [;
      SitAny: <<Enter ChapterBenches>>;
    ],
    cheap_scenery
      1 'scroll' "It's just a painted part of the statue.",
  has
    ;


Chair -> ChapterBenches "benches"                              ! >ChapterBenches
